&= a_1 x(1-x)(1+x) + a_2 y(1-y)(1+y) + xy (1-x) a_4 \\
&= a_1 x(1 - x)(1 + x) + a_2 y(1 - y)(1 + y) - \left( \frac{3}{2} a_1 + \frac{3}{2} a_2 \right) xy(1 - x) \\
